Targeting_Reticule.targetHelp: You have been targeted by the War Walker, and are now susceptible to more of its attacks.

Extinction.targetHelp: Once engaged in combat, the Extinction War Walker must continue to be engaged in combat or it will eliminate all resistance instantly.
Extinction.attackerAttackFloater: You have failed to defeat the War Walker
Extinction.victimHit: You have been defeated! Once engaged in combat, the Extinction War Walker must continue to be engaged in combat or it will eliminate all resistance instantly.

messages.attackerHit: You hit {PlayerDest} with your {PowerName} for {Damage} points of Energy damage over time.
messages.victimHit: {PlayerSource} hits you with their {PowerName} for {Damage} points of Energy damage over time.

Arrest_Mode.help: Causes a PBAoE Hold to emit from everyone who has a Targeting Reticle.

Lethal_Force_Authorized.help: Causes a PBAoE DoT to emit from everyone who has a Targeting Reticle.
Lethal_Force_Authorized.targetHelp: The WarWalker has sprayed you with burning plasma.

Crowd_Dispersal.help: Causes a PBAoE Terrorize to emit from everyone who has a Targeting Reticle.
